 I mean all I wanted was to go to the Liberal }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9324736\charrsid7434366 T}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 
