\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9324736\charrsid7434366 T}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 ea. I suppose my father had told him when he went round canvassing that he should vote Liberal.
