\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7038994 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 
Well not exactly had to but you may be sure he did. But he wasn't a man to argue or take any special interest, you know, or argue about it, he never put any bills in his window or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81562 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 You don't remember any political discussions in the home. Your parents had about politics?
