ll doctors and say professional people, even successful business people. I mean a man might be a grocer, he'd got er well prosperous grocer's business, well if he could he'd sent his boy to grammar school you see, and they were the type, but between them 
and well if there was a girl's, there was a girl's school there too, well one or two private but between that there was nothing.
