Oh yes, you got some that were very poor. You see they came from extremely big families and often if the father was out of work people had a rough time because there was no unemployment pay and well ther
e was just nothing. Unemployment was just the thing that was dreaded and if, course, if the father was out of work well they were poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81562 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 Well at your school, did you, do you remember children who struggled all the time?
