\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81562 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 They'd shout this out would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7038994 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 Oh they would sometimes you see because children were rude. In some ways they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81562 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 Yes, yes,. In your school, did you ever have any prizes at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7038994 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 
Oh yes, you had, you had a prize for attendance, every year if you were, but you didn't get prizes for work not then, and you also, at Sunday school you had prizes. They were always books, you never
 had anything else. I had a whole collection, oh yes, I had a whole.. but of course they all got worn out, but I did I had a whole collection. Of course the Sunday School books were generally very \{ILLEGIBLE\} of course.
