\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7038994 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 Yes, well you see the whole thing was, yes, we
 just did, we were lucky enough to have the health that we didn't have to stop away. Besides if you did stop away you had the attendance officer round, oh yes you couldn't stop away lightly.
