ell if they weren't married they were all away working you see, so we didn't need so much room really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81562 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 That was when you were 10, I think you said about? You were about 10 years old when you moved.
