\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81562 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11816647\charrsid7434366 In your first home how did you sleep in the family, I mean with the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4000104\charrsid7434366 2}{
